chapter/045-json-object.html.body:
JSON Object
JSON Object功能基本与js一致。
初始化
// way 1
obj = {}

// way 2
obj = {name:"tom", age: 88}

// way 3
color = "strawberry"
obj = {
    name: "car",
    special: "carry",
    food: "oil",
    colors: ["red", color, "black"]
}

键值数量获取
obj = {name:"tom", age: 88}
println(obj.size()) // 2

键值添加
obj = {}
// way 1
obj["name"] = "jerry"
// way 2
obj.age = 3
println(obj) // {"name":"jerry", "age":3}

值修改
obj = {"name":"jerry", "age":3}
// way 1
obj["name"] = "tom"
// way 2
obj.age = 18
println(obj) // {"name":"tom", "age":18}

键值删除
obj = {name:"tom", age: 88}
obj.remove("age")
println(obj) // {"name":"tom"}

判断是否包含相应键
obj = {name:"tom", age: 88}
println(obj.contain("name")) // true
println(obj.contain("addr")) // false

遍历
obj = {name:"tom", age: 88}
foreach k, v : obj {
    println(k, v)
}

输出
age 88
name tom
JSON Object 方法



方法
描述




size()
键值对数量


remove(key)
根据指定键移除键值对


contain(key))
判断是否包含相应键

